title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Jocelyn Suryasaputra
text:
Makanan sehat yang tetap enak, buka pagi jadi bisa buat opsi sarapan. Pelayanan nya cepat dan ramah, pernah denger cerita kalau Madame Chang di buka karena kisah dari owner nya, jadi yakin kalau makanan nya ga overclaim.

Untuk harga lumayan pricey, tapi dari segi bahan keliatan kalau yang di pakai premium semua. Telur yang di pakai benar” orange, telur omega. Daging dan bawang-bawang nya fresh semua😍 Mereka sedia dessert juga, dari yang local, peranakan, western juga ada!

Parkir juga guede pol, di sebelah nya persis ada 1 lahan khusus buat parkiran. Dinning area juga bersih pol, selama ini makan di Madame Chang belum ada keluhan mengenai kebersihan, cutleries, piring, sampe toilet semua kinclong! Good job!

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Bob Mulyate
text:
Salah satu resto/cafe yang sudah melegenda di Surabaya. Terkenal karena menu-menu nya yang sehat. Seperti minuman barley, lemongrass tea, lo han guo, dan lain lain. Semua menu yang dijual tanpa MSG, pengawet, dan pemanis buatan.

Area parkir cukup untuk beberapa mobil.

Tersedia seating area indoor yang banyak. Tempat nya dingin dan nyaman.

Untuk menu sangat variatif, dari nasi, mie, sides, buah, pentol, siomay, dan lain lain. Ada beberapa showcase chiller berisi aneka macam minuman yang bisa kita pilih. Untuk dessert juga ada berbagai macam es dan pudding.

Madame Chang cocok untuk segala usia dan juga cocok untuk makan pagi/ makan siang/ makan malam/ atau sekedar cemilan.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Yusuf Irwantono
text: Lokasi di kawasan kuliner Surabaya Barat. Tempatnya cukup luas. Parkir sangat luas karena di sebelahnya ada tempat parkir lagi. Resto ini terkenal karena no MSG, no pengawet, seperti ikon makanan sehat di Surabaya. Tapi menurut saya ga 100% makanan sehat, cuman memang lebih terasa sehat dibanding resto lainnya. Karena rasanya, antara ga suka atau suka banget. Sebelum pesan disuruh scan yang akan diarahkan ke whatsappnya untuk ketik pesan baru bisa lihat menunya. Minta aja menu fisiknya kalau gamau whatsapp. Kami pesan Sesame Chicken (ayam wijen), Madame Chang's Rice (nasi ayam), Madame Chang's Rolls (salad dengan udang/ayam), Dragon ball (pentol kocok), Yummy Soursoup (es sirsak), Wintermelon ballen. Ayam wijen saus hijau enak banget. Wangi wijen, ayamnya empuk, bumbu hijaunya gak ada obat enak banget. Kayaknya pakai minyak bawang juga. Di sini enaknya bisa nambah bumbunya dan bawang goreng sepuasnya. Make sure untuk aduk ayamnya, karena minyak wijennya di bawah. Nasi ayamnya juga enak, ada sambal bangkoknya. Bisa pilih nasi merah atau nasi putih. Salad enak, ada udangnya. Bumbu cocolnya seperti mengandung kacang, menurut saya enak. Pentolnya cukup enak, gorengannya kurang mantap kalau saya. Pentolnya teksturnya bukan yang kenyal banget. Gak ada bumbu kacangnya. Adanya kecap, sambal, jangan lupa kasi jeruk nipis dan bawang gorengnya. Agak beda sama pentol yg biasa beli di jalanan. Wintermelon enak, ada di kulkas, ga terlalu manis. Mereka jg terkenal akan dessert dan minumannya biasa orang bungkus banyak. Termasuk mahal menurut saya tapi worth it. Harga sudah termasuk tax bagusnya. Overall sangat recommended.

saya kemarin pesan mie goreng (madame Chang's dry noodle), mie kuah (madame chang's noodle soup), es serut sirsat (yummy soursop) dan es serut mangga (manggo sensasion) dan rasanya tidak mengecewakan, enak dan segar...
lokasi strategis dan mudah dicari, di Jl. Raya Darmo Permai I no.15, Surabaya Barat
parkir banyak di depan dan disebelah restoran juga, cuma yg depan jika parkir dibelakang mobil orang, enak enaknya makan suka dipanggil karena mobil depan kita mau keluar...wkkk

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Steve Isaac
text:
Huge thanks to my great friend, William, on taking me here for breakfast.

What a well designed restaurant, specially love how they showcase their drinks respectively. From non-sweet to regular sweet. A real healthy approach 👍🏻

The food we ate was extremely spot on for my taste bud 🤤 not one miss their mark.

Servers seem well trained down to explaining how to eat certain dishes and very informative on their menu.

Well done management in giving me an impressive 1st dining experience here 🙏🏻 I thank you.

Highly recommended and couldn't wait to return and try their other dishes✨

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Jeanne
text:
Madame Chang is a restaurant that has established a strong presence in the culinary and healthy food industry. It offers a wide variety of drinks and desserts that are unique and delicious. Additionally, their main dishes are also healthy and high in fiber, making them suitable for a nutritious meal. One of my favorite menu items here is the "pentol" (dragon ball) because of its chewy texture and crispy fried coating. The ambiance of the restaurant is bright and perfect for dining with family or friends.

Please note that this review is based on my personal experience and may not reflect the current state of the restaurant. It's always a good idea to visit and experience it for yourself.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Danny Kwan
text: This place easily deserve a 5 star rating. They serves good healthy yet delicious foods and their dessert are so unique and also refreshing. The interior inside feels so clean and bright with green as main color. All and all most of their menu are super recommended. Will come again when have the chance

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Fararine Margaretta
text:
They serve healthy food with great taste. Really recommend their sesame chicken!

I also reccommend their Kimchi Cold Noodle! Please choose the Cold one instead if the hot.
It's so refreshing! *if you like kimchi of course*

Today, I tried Tahu Gejrot! Their tofu is baked not fried. Consider it healthier than the usual Tahu Gejrot.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Si Doel
text:
Resto cukup lama di Surabaya di era 2000-an. Ramainya bisa luar biasa dan parkiran full. Kadang pesan delivery.

Biasa pesan menu favorit shrimp rolls, nasi ayam bumbu sereh, pentol kocok, bubur. Minuman rempah/herbal biasa yang saya pesan lemongrass tea, barley, dan alang2 ijo. Dessert fu chuk, cheng teng, dan mango sensation.

Pentol dragon ball juga suka banget tapi biasanya pilih yg lebih banyak gorengannya dibandingkan pentolnya karena lebih enak. Parkiran luas, tempatnya nyaman, ada ac dan bisa pilih langsung di kulkas besar kalau mau pesen minum, overall tipikal makanan enak dan sehat.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai

Estimasi 50k-75k/person. Parkir luas, tempat bersih. Toilet hanya sepasang. Sering harus antri untuk ke toilet.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: joy tourtravel
text:
Madam Chang ini terkenal dgn pentolnya yg higienis. Kalau orang yang memperhatikan masalah kebersihan dan kualitas makanan, mereka kadang kepengen makan pentol tapi takut karena mungkin kualitas dagingnya tidak jelas dan juga beli di pinggir jalan rada susah. Nah ini menurut saya adalah salah satu kelebihan dari Madam Chang, bisa melihat potensi bisnis ini. Walaupun kesannya remeh temeh, ah cuma pentol, tapi dengan apa yang ditawarkan disini sangat baik dan memuaskan pelanggan. Apalagi jika kita kedatangan tamu dari luar kota bahkan luar negri, ingin ngajak mereka makan pentol dengan tempat dan suasana yang nyaman, hanya ada disini. Bawang gorengnya juga enak, cara packagingnya juga bagus bahkan ada disiapin pentol kemasan isi 50 bj yg bisa dibawa pulang atau mungkin buat oleh-oleh. Selain pentol, ada bbrp menu lain juga yang diandalkan, misalnya manisan mangganya atau mungkin dessertnya.
Jadi yg mau makan pentol tapi bisa sambil ngerumpi dan gak keringatan di jalanan, bisa mampir disini :)

The best drink is barley.  not sweet but so good🤤

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Mrs. NJ
text: A restaurant that serves Taiwan cuisines. Their signature is Madame Chang's Rice, which is simply rice with shreded fried chicken, egg, and salad. The taste is quite delicious. Their salad also fresh and tasty. Here, you can also find many kinds of dessert an beverages. This place is crowded especially on Saturday and Sunday nights.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Mar Su
text:
This restaurant boasts their variety of msg free foods. Their dragonball (pentolan) is not bad because they are super generous in giving the shallots. Their special sesame chicken is only available during the weekends (minimal size is half chicken), good for sharing. Spicy minced chicken rice is like thai's Pad ka prow (minced basil chicken).    Madame chang rice is basically grilled chicken marinated in ginger, lemongrass (the smell can be overwhelming to some).

They have several variety of desserts and drinks like cheng teng, puddings, thai tea... i really hate Chop chop (jackfruit, avocado and coconut) - this supposedly "es teler" looks cold, but its NOT THAT COLD (definitely not going to have that again).

Overall this place is popular among health conscious folks. Parking space is pretty spacious, they have a plot next door. Considering some price, ambience and serving, I will rate it a 4*/5*

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Boon Loong Leo
text:
This restaurant was quite near where I stayed while in Surabaya, although it still need transportation ie. Car. Getting around Indonesia is still relatively troublesome without a car.

Advocating themselves as health food restaurant, the foods here were less oily and purportedly healthier options. Their siomay (how they called siew Mai) are basically two pieces cut into 8 parts; I quite like their dumlling soup as the meat portion was quite generous; but the star dish was their poached ayam kampung topped generously with coriander as it was tender and sweet tasting.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Mariska A
text:
Kali2 makan sehat yuk, uda sekian lama makannya makanan pada umumnya. Waktunya mengistirahatkan perut buat makan sehat
.
.
.
Rasa : bintang tiga
Harga : Bervariatif tergantung menu, in frame :
1. Madame Chang’s Noodles Soup Rp. 45.000,-
2. Wonton Soup Rp.35.000,-
3. Madame Chang’s Dragon Ball aka pentol elit Rp.22.000,-
4. Madame Chang’s Chicken Rice Rp. 45.000,-
5.Madame Chang’s Kimchi Noodles Cold Rp.56.000,-
6. Madame Chang’s J- Rice Rp.30.000,-
.
.
.
exclude tax
.
.
.
Lokasi : @madame_chang (Jl. Raya Darmo Permai I/15 Surabaya)
.
.
Buka: Setiap hari (pkl.08.00 wib- pkl.22.00 wib)
.
.
.
@madame_chang tempat makan khusus menyediakan makanan sehat. Selain non MSG, @madame_chang juga pakai bahan dengan kualitas terjamin. Secara tempat, @madame_chang termasuk bersih dan nyaman. Oya @madame_chang Termasuk salah satu tempat makan favorit. Kok tau? Iya soalnya kalau ke sini musti siap2 antri baik antri parkir maupun antri tempat duduk. Untung pelayanannya cukup cepat dan tanggap jadi begitu ada tempat kosong langsung dilanyanin. Well balik ke menu di atas, untuk @madame_chang noodles nya pakai mie besar (kaya udon) dan mie putih kecil. Secara  rasa cukup gurih asin sama seperti rasa wonton soup nya. Untuk wonton Soup nya, kalau dilihat porsinya keliatannya kaya kecil padahal bisa bikin perut kenyang lo hahaha Oya satu lagi menu dari @madame_chang yg mana itu adalah cemilan khasnya Surabaya “Pentol”, pentol di sini sebutannya pentol elit/ @madame_chang ’s dragon ball. Yang unik dari pentolnya selain dari bahan, kita diberi kebebasan untuk racik bumbunya sendiri loh. @madame_chang menyediakan sambal, kecap dan bawang goreng.
Nah buat pecinta kuliner healthy food / yg mau makan healthy food, cobain gih ke @madame_chang . Selamat mencoba dan happy eating

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Chandra Soetanto
text: Everything here is considered healthy food, cooked well without MSG. Not much meal choices. Few rice and noodle menus, some salads, soups, and desserts. Unique serving and taste. Also has some good vegetarian option and healthy tea. There is valet service available, so parking won't be a problem when it's crowded.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai

Many choices of desert and drink.
I'll give five stars when they are able to improve on the service time and friendliness from the waitress.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Andi Anto
text:
There are 2 type of people.
1. Loved the Madame Chang food.
2. Taste it once and will never come back again.

My wife loved it so much, give it 5 star and always recommended it to her friends and family. She drag me in to try, said that it was healthy and delicious.

When i tried it, well it was not my taste. I almost can't eat anything in there, i felt like an Alien in earth just staring other people eating voraciously. I give 1 star for it.

So 5 star and 1 star. Divide it by 2 people and Madame Chang got 3 star.

title: Madame Chang Darmo Permai
name: Kedar Tembe
text: Not too many options. Went there because it was the first vegan place in the list I googled, but it isn't vegan; just has a few vegan options. Had some mushroom and tofu rice dumpling and potato chips, and was just ok. Was just happy finding something vegan in surbaya. The coconut kefir was excellent though. Clean and trendy place i think. But again, for vegans, not too many options
